---
import Layout from '../layouts/AboutLayout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Me"
	description="A passionate Full-Stack Developer specializing in creating beautiful and engaging user experiences."
>
	<div class="space-y-8">
		<section>
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">About Me</h2>
			<p class="mt-4 text-lg">
				I'm a passionate Full-Stack Developer with a specialization in creating beautiful, highly
				interactive, and engaging user experiences on the front-end. With a strong foundation in modern
				web technologies, I excel at bringing ideas to life, from the initial concept and design to
				implementation and deployment.
			</p>
			<p class="mt-4 text-lg">
				My approach is driven by a constant desire for innovation and a commitment to writing clean,
				efficient, and maintainable code. I thrive on solving complex problems and am dedicated to a
				lifelong journey of learning and experimentation in the ever-evolving world of web development.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Languages</h3>
			<p class="mt-2">
				Italian (native), English (15+ years of experience), Spanish (5+ years of experience)
			</p>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Education</h3>
			<ul class="mt-2 list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
				<li>
					<strong>Popular Music and Recording</strong> (2014-2015), Salford University, Manchester,
					England
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>Electronic Music</strong> (2016-2019), Conservatorio Licinio Refice, Frosinone, Italy
					<em>(Bachelor Degree)</em>
				</li>
				<li><strong>Design Study Abroad</strong> (2020), ELISAVA, Barcelona, Spain</li>
				<li>
					<strong>Cognitive Systems and Interactive Media (CSIM)</strong> (2021-2022), Universitat
					Pompeu Fabra, Barcelona, Spain <em>(Master Degree)</em>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Publications</h3>
			<ul class="mt-2 list-disc list-inside">
				<li>
					Micozzi Ferri, Lorenzo.
					<em>I know what you type: empathy in real-time typed Computer Mediated Communication.</em>
					2022,
					<a href="http://hdl.handle.net/10230/54272" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="underline"
						>http://hdl.handle.net/10230/54272</a
					>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Teaching and Talks</h3>
			<ul class="mt-2 list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
				<li>“Introduzione alla modellazione 3D in Blender”, I.I.S. Marconi, Civitavecchia, RM, Italy (2019)</li>
				<li>“Chordata Motion Capture technology”, L.E.V. MATADERO, Madrid, Spain (2021)</li>
				<li>“Status Quo Selfie. El autorretrato como análisis profundo”, Ideas Digitales, Madrid, Spain (2021)</li>
				<li>
					“Space transformer cookbook, trasformare gli spazi urbani attraverso principi di game design.”,
					WelcomeToDaFuture, Rome, Italy (2023)
				</li>
			</ul>
		</section>
	</div>
</Layout>
